definitions.definition: One of a group that acts in harmony; a person who is part of a conspiracy .
Part of a group that agree to do an unlawful or unethical act.
examples: The conspirators were rounded up by the police and arrested.

main_definition: One of a group that acts in harmony; a person who is part of a conspiracy .
secondary_definitions: Part of a group that agree to do an unlawful or unethical act.
